column5: Somebody posted pics of a guy with a hook in his eye. It was about a couple months ago, but I don't know the exact date. Is it possible I can view these pictures again? Thanks.
I don't think you can access the old galleries anymore, you might be able to find it doing a websearch...  Mike
My Gawd! Why would anyone want to see that? That's too terrible to even imagine.
It takes all kinds Roy,java script:emoticon('', 'smid_24')
